988
00:40:10,540 --> 00:40:11,580
It's too tiring.

989
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:14,460
Don't talk about that.

990
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,740
I'm supposed to care for you

991
00:40:15,740 --> 00:40:16,980
